{"tid":697342,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"當賭錢麻木到一個點既時候你地用咩野堅持落去","createTime":"2018-06-11T02:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T08:58:00.000Z","uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"595b5deea936f1fc88185e5eccf1e443371c9458","tid":697342,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:02:43.000Z","msg":"當第一注後,隨住時間輸輸贏贏但總數都還是大輸時你地點解仲要賭落去?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家係麻木到一個當將錢當左一個數字,輸嬴沒甚反感,我覺得好大部份係因為現實生活中既挫敗而去賭錢,奇怪既係唔是想從中獲得什麼,只係從熟悉的某種行為中可以有個習慣去做<br />\n賭錢只係一種習慣既日常行為,因為習慣左唔好去改變"},{"pid":"297dcf12b1e871882dfacf909f178de304a35256","tid":697342,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:11:35.000Z","msg":"刺激感"},{"pid":"46478d0a3128a465802b8c806a4c0392fe7f5cbf","tid":697342,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:12:47.000Z","msg":"就黎定輸嬴個種feel爽撚過屌閪"},{"pid":"2155bed0d6315e3b90d41116817871fe145a65e4","tid":697342,"uid":134128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"輸到無咩感覺"},{"pid":"9b26cd9959c20e0d51e36abe3c9b829234e5dfef","tid":697342,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46478d0a3128a465802b8c806a4c0392fe7f5cbf","tid":697342,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:12:47.000Z","msg":"就黎定輸嬴個種feel爽撚過屌閪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"輸多嬴少呢"},{"pid":"2a2e8e2d89f8fd02320c58a33dbb968ccbcf7300","tid":697342,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2155bed0d6315e3b90d41116817871fe145a65e4","tid":697342,"uid":134128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"輸到無咩感覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:23:51.000Z","msg":"習慣化 就好似只係上網按一個鍵掣咁 好平常"},{"pid":"514daacf649689c7155bbf2248a3c9f89cd04468","tid":697342,"uid":79686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"好常惡改<br />\n<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"3188c506063fd5f1db42ee922f62889185c9b9df","tid":697342,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"當返工"},{"pid":"9771f8eeb7f23abbf5d3fbdf5d3f00221fad4a72","tid":697342,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ecee7d11546b3f194644fa5c353b82bf306bde","tid":697342,"uid":155197,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"聽住無盡黎賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輸錢：曾懷著心底的信仰 千次萬次跌傷<br />\n開始不敢回頭尋覓那真相<br />\n自我安慰：踏上這無盡旅途 過去飄散消散失散花火<br />\n重拾賭博：或許到最後沒有完美句號<br />\n仍然倔強冒險一一去征討<br />\n落注：合十雙手去禱告<br />\n贏錢：天空尚有片夕陽帶領<br />\n再賭：來提步 壯闊跑道<br />\n可以無限loop"},{"pid":"7b5d851d95cea280f4f0b4d2c283a208e18901af","tid":697342,"uid":73598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:43:48.000Z","msg":"係窮呀，屌你個閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6862eabc44fafd685b9ab953352b917f7d7dbe97","tid":697342,"uid":51948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"同巴打一樣 但最近都戒緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實冇必要繼續賭落去<br />\n以前一場接一場咁賭 贏既keep係馬會到 最後都連本輸埋 但冇乜感覺繼續賭 只係享受賭個時既過程<br />\n不過開始賭到瞓唔到 返工集中唔到 銀行戶口啲錢差唔多輸哂 開始意識到再賭落去唔係辦法 <br />\n而家寧願攞啲錢去食餐好都唔想拎去賭"},{"pid":"4ec837b092f9c5fe8a0ad8bdc55103ab7eaa4a3e","tid":697342,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"平時食個buffet 都左度右度<br />\n賭個陣就幾皮幾皮咁鳩買都覺無問題..."},{"pid":"8b2b6bf2936c3da80e983500c3e6f8b7299e633b","tid":697342,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ec837b092f9c5fe8a0ad8bdc55103ab7eaa4a3e","tid":697342,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"平時食個buffet 都左度右度<br />\n賭個陣就幾皮幾皮咁鳩買都覺無問題..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"的確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢種是患了病"},{"pid":"da7d677b347379d83861a004c543eb6c05a9ea53","tid":697342,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:19:58.000Z","msg":"未輸過 答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8010fa30404cb958875cde39e9e537a46ff5026","tid":697342,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"595b5deea936f1fc88185e5eccf1e443371c9458","tid":697342,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:02:43.000Z","msg":"當第一注後,隨住時間輸輸贏贏但總數都還是大輸時你地點解仲要賭落去?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家係麻木到一個當將錢當左一個數字,輸嬴沒甚反感,我覺得好大部份係因為現實生活中既挫敗而去賭錢,奇怪既係唔是想從中獲得什麼,只係從熟悉的某種行為中可以有個習慣去做<br />\n賭錢只係一種習慣既日常行為,因為習慣左唔好去改變"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"Bro, 既然你都醒覺,覺得依個賭嘅習慣唔好, 咁你想唔想戒呀?"},{"pid":"2a67cd40ae9cf70688be23458aacade9b2c17f1b","tid":697342,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6862eabc44fafd685b9ab953352b917f7d7dbe97","tid":697342,"uid":51948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"同巴打一樣 但最近都戒緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實冇必要繼續賭落去<br />\n以前一場接一場咁賭 贏既keep係馬會到 最後都連本輸埋 但冇乜感覺繼續賭 只係享受賭個時既過程<br />\n不過開始賭到瞓唔到 返工集中唔到 銀行戶口啲錢差唔多輸哂 開始意識到再賭落去唔係辦法 <br />\n而家寧願攞啲錢去食餐好都唔想拎去賭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"Bro, 你好叻呀, 有戒賭嘅決心, 離開一個已經跟左你好耐嘅習慣一定好唔容易...<br />\n你依加D 睡眠有冇好轉呀?"},{"pid":"ef5d233ecf818e320708eac2505a91eddc08de71","tid":697342,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8010fa30404cb958875cde39e9e537a46ff5026","tid":697342,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"595b5deea936f1fc88185e5eccf1e443371c9458","tid":697342,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:02:43.000Z","msg":"當第一注後,隨住時間輸輸贏贏但總數都還是大輸時你地點解仲要賭落去?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\